-- Pingdingshan Tianan Says Eight Killed in Accident at One of Its Coal Mines
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-28T22:46:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/pingdingshan-tianan-says-eight-killed-in-accident-at-one-of-its-coal-mines.html

          
          
             Pingdingshan Tianan Coal Mining Co.
said eight people died in an accident at one of the company’s
mines, according to a filing to Shanghai’s stock exchange.
Losses resulting from the accident will be announced later,
according to the statement, which didn’t give additional
details.  
